  "title": "Design Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Job Duties & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Carry out civil / structural design (knowledge in steel structure preferred)</li><li>Prepare calculations / plans for submission to Main Contractor.</li><li>Prepare shop drawings.</li><li>Manage projects’ design</li><li>Liaising with internal stakeholder on work procedure and design implications.</li><li>Attend Projects & Consultants Meetings</li><li>Providing technical advice</li><li>Liaising with relevant professional staff such as Main Contractor’s ERSS QP/ AC</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree/Post Graduate Diploma/Professional Degree in Engineering (Civil) or equivalent.</li><li>Register Structural Steel Engineer (StEr) (Preferred)</li><li>Familiar with Eurocode (Preferred)</li><li>Background in construction design (Preferred)</li><li>Familiar with Steel Structure design</li><li>Familiar with Euro Code</li><li>Familiar with Engineering Software</li><li>Familiar with Autocad</li><li>IT Literate able to use Microsoft Office and Microsoft Project</li><li>Good command of written and spoken English</li></ul>",
